n a negotiation and wish you know how to read body language. Invest the time in this course and you will be happy to have a leg up on your communication in the future.\r\n\r\nIf you wish you could begin to unravel the mysteries of body language, then enroll today in Secrets of Body Language now!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Course certificates\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][stm_color_separator][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][stm_certificate image=\"1490\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][stm_certificate image=\"1490\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Course overview\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\" css=\".vc_custom_1436944848385{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][stm_course_lessons title=\" Section 1: Introduction\"][stm_course_lesson icon=\"fa-icon-stm_icon_teacher\" badge=\"free\" title=\"Introduction\" meta=\"Preview\" meta_icon=\"fa fa-youtube-play\"]Here is a brief overview to the course and what you will learn![/stm_course_lesson][stm_course_lesson icon=\"fa fa-female\" badge=\"preview\" title=\"Body Language Challenge \" meta=\"Preview\" meta_icon=\"fa fa-youtube-play\"]I have 2 body language challenges for you:\r\n\r\n1. I want you to test your skills from the beginning to the end of the course. We are going to watch 2 videos now and then watch them again at the end of the course, where we will slow them down and dissect the body language.\r\n\r\n2. Sign-Up to get free practice videos to test your skills:\r\n\r\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.scienceofpeople.com/subscribe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">ScienceofPeople.com</a>\r\n\r\nReply to the first email and<s